    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know there are people to call, but they just tell you to keep holding on. but why? just to endure more of this? it feels like everyone is just asking me to be a martyr for a life i dont even recognize anymore. if there's no way to fix it, isn't it just more compassionate to let someone rest when they've clearly had enough? it feels like a mercy, doesn't it?",
